    <p>Large tables are easier to parse visually if rows are easily distinguishable. Adding the {{code "yui3-table-odd"}} class name to every other {{code "<tr>"}} element changes the background of the row and creates a zebra-styled effect.</p>

    {{> tables/striped}}

